name: Medusa Panda - KuD-049
description: Her story came from ancient greek in pandas universe. She is the daughter of Phorcys and Ceto and known as one of the three gorgons with a living snake on her head. She is beautiful yet terrifying, her gaze is so dangerous. They say she can turn anybody who look into her to stone. She used to be a beautiful maiden at first, but she got punished by athena's because of her bad deed and thats where snake on her head came from. Many adore her, but many feared her too.
